_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/953060/extras/1067f780dcda32a872c4fcf1dacaf8f7.webp?t=1728985937\" width=48 height=48 /></span> The game features cutting-edge software technologies as well. Starting in 2009, you can build blockchain projects.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/953060/extras/1067f780dcda32a872c4fcf1dacaf8f7.webp?t=1728985937\" width=48 height=48 /></span> We did our best to make the timeline as realistic as possible. Have fun and learn new facts simultaneously. </p>",
